  "detailed_description": "Balocks is a casual arcade game designed for those who enjoy arranging pieces without leaving spaces. With a unique twist, you move all the pieces simultaneously! Combine pieces in a 4x4 block or larger to clear them and earn points. Enhance your combo, aim for a high score, and unlock new backgrounds and palettes as you progress!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/3e9fdcd81341931f87492143c2eb18f2.poster.avif?t=1724356852\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/3e9fdcd81341931f87492143c2eb18f2.webm?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/3e9fdcd81341931f87492143c2eb18f2.mp4?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2>Balocks features two game modes: <br><br>In <strong>Normal Mode</strong>, challenge yourself to achieve high scores by clearing blocks and maintaining your combo within a 5-minute limit. Every move counts, can you think fast and score high when the clock is ticking?<br><br>For a more relaxed experience, try <strong>Zen Mode</strong>. You can play without worrying about scores or losing. Just enjoy merging blocks at your own pace. Zen Mode is perfect for unwinding after a long day or just to enjoy the flow of the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/fa817f8d18aa4aa84bd4f76f8ac9b192.poster.avif?t=1724356852\" width=600 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/fa817f8d18aa4aa84bd4f76f8ac9b192.webm?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/fa817f8d18aa4aa84bd4f76f8ac9b192.mp4?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Style Customization</h2>Personalize your experience with a variety of backgrounds and color variations for the block pieces. Make the game follow your style!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/736046cd0215f9cd835840c2f2719974.poster.avif?t=1724356852\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/736046cd0215f9cd835840c2f2719974.webm?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/736046cd0215f9cd835840c2f2719974.mp4?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Balocks is a casual arcade game designed for those who enjoy arranging pieces without leaving spaces. With a unique twist, you move all the pieces simultaneously! Combine pieces in a 4x4 block or larger to clear them and earn points. Enhance your combo, aim for a high score, and unlock new backgrounds and palettes as you progress!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/3e9fdcd81341931f87492143c2eb18f2.poster.avif?t=1724356852\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/3e9fdcd81341931f87492143c2eb18f2.webm?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/3e9fdcd81341931f87492143c2eb18f2.mp4?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2>Balocks features two game modes: <br><br>In <strong>Normal Mode</strong>, challenge yourself to achieve high scores by clearing blocks and maintaining your combo within a 5-minute limit. Every move counts, can you think fast and score high when the clock is ticking?<br><br>For a more relaxed experience, try <strong>Zen Mode</strong>. You can play without worrying about scores or losing. Just enjoy merging blocks at your own pace. Zen Mode is perfect for unwinding after a long day or just to enjoy the flow of the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/fa817f8d18aa4aa84bd4f76f8ac9b192.poster.avif?t=1724356852\" width=600 height=88 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/fa817f8d18aa4aa84bd4f76f8ac9b192.webm?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/fa817f8d18aa4aa84bd4f76f8ac9b192.mp4?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Style Customization</h2>Personalize your experience with a variety of backgrounds and color variations for the block pieces. Make the game follow your style!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/736046cd0215f9cd835840c2f2719974.poster.avif?t=1724356852\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/736046cd0215f9cd835840c2f2719974.webm?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103340/extras/736046cd0215f9cd835840c2f2719974.mp4?t=1724356852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
